We currently support the following cloud providers in test_matrix_run job Manual mode:
- "AWS", alias self-managed AWS
- "GCP", alias self-managed GCP
- "Managed AWS", alias OSD alias OSD/AWS
- "Managed GCP", alias OSD alial OSD/GCP
- "PSI", alias OpenStack OCP

Additional Notes:
- TEST_PLATFORM: The "Managed" clustes can be provisioned in 2 test platforms: stage and prod
- SINGLE_NODE_OPENSHIFT: self-managed clusters - except for PSI - can be provisioned with one single node